Package com.flopsar.api.fdbc

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Connection
    The API interface provides basic methods to access all the data in the Flopsar database.
    ConnectionFactory.ExtractProgress
    Progress callback interface.
    FindEvent<T>
    A user must implement this interface so that they can process data that are passed in the FindEvent.onFound(Object).
    MethodInvocation
    Value holder interface, representing a method invocation.
    MethodInvocationTree
    Represents a methods execution tree.
    MethodInvocationTreeItem
    Represents a method invocation element in the methods execution tree.
    MetricValue
    Value holder interface representing a metric of a single value.
    Symbol
    An object representing a generic symbol.
